1
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:10,000
Master,

2
00:00:21,640 --> 00:00:22,880
it's really you!

3
00:00:23,840 --> 00:00:24,880
You're still alive!

4
00:00:26,040 --> 00:00:26,640
Don't cry.

5
00:00:27,160 --> 00:00:28,560
Look, I'm fine.

6
00:00:29,320 --> 00:00:30,720
Then why are you here?

7
00:00:31,680 --> 00:00:33,520
Why haven't you ever contacted me?

8
00:00:34,520 --> 00:00:36,000
I couldn't put you in danger.

9
00:00:37,280 --> 00:00:39,480
I've been secretly investigating

10
00:00:39,560 --> 00:00:41,920
the source and network of Pang Zhengsong's obedience water.

11
00:00:42,720 --> 00:00:43,320
So...

12
00:00:44,480 --> 00:00:44,840
What...

13
00:00:45,120 --> 00:00:46,120
What's going on?

14
00:00:46,360 --> 00:00:47,600
I saw you...

15
00:00:48,880 --> 00:00:49,920
It was Pang Jingfu!

16
00:00:53,800 --> 00:00:54,440
What?

17
00:00:54,440 --> 00:00:55,480
What do you mean?

18
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:17,320
You're awake.

19
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:19,360
You look good.

20
00:01:19,680 --> 00:01:20,400
Why are you here?

21
00:01:20,720 --> 00:01:21,480
Where's Pang Jingfu?

22
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:26,560
This is also part of Brother Fu's plan.

23
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:28,080
Plan?

24
00:01:28,240 --> 00:01:29,680
The gun is specially made.

25
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:30,640
It looks scary.

26
00:01:30,960 --> 00:01:32,960
I brought you here as soon as you died.

27
00:01:33,160 --> 00:01:34,320
You saved me?

28
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:37,880
I'm not that kind.

29
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:39,520
It's Brother Fu who saved you.

30
00:01:40,040 --> 00:01:41,520
He planned to fake your death

31
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:43,960
to cover up Master Pang's suspicion of him.

32
00:01:44,880 --> 00:01:46,120
Brother Fu

33
00:01:46,440 --> 00:01:47,520
didn't want you to die.

34
00:01:48,880 --> 00:01:49,560
So he

35
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:51,440
never really wanted to kill you.

36
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:53,960
He lied to me,

37
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:55,720
and his father.

38
00:01:56,880 --> 00:01:58,760
He did all this for...

39
00:01:58,800 --> 00:01:59,520
Yes.

40
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:02,720
To root out his father and the evil network

41
00:02:02,720 --> 00:02:03,760
behind him.

42
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:05,400
I only knew the truth after reporting to the Director.

43
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:10,720
You did it to protect me.

44
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:13,360
Pang Jingfu.

45
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:33,040
Go to sleep.

46
00:02:33,040 --> 00:02:37,480
My dear baby.

47
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:42,200
My hands

48
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:46,760
will always protect you.

49
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:01,680
Instead of letting you die,

50
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:04,400
this is more interesting, right?

51
00:03:09,040 --> 00:03:09,800
Yan.

52
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:10,880
I've sent you the password to the room.

53
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,240
[You must save Brother Fu.]

54
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:25,240
Pang Jingfu.

55
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:31,480
Don't come over.

56
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:33,320
Don't come over.

57
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:38,840
It's me.

58
00:03:39,880 --> 00:03:41,120
It's okay. It's okay. Don't.

59
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:43,280
I don't want you to see me like this.

60
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:47,800
It's okay. It's okay.

61
00:03:54,640 --> 00:03:56,360
Go. Pang Jingfu, it's me. Don't be afraid.

62
00:03:56,760 --> 00:03:57,160
Tian Yan.

63
00:03:57,160 --> 00:03:57,720
Don't be afraid.

64
00:03:58,200 --> 00:03:59,240
Don't see me like this.

65
00:03:59,240 --> 00:03:59,760
I'm here.

66
00:03:59,760 --> 00:04:00,320
Go.

67
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:01,600
Go.

68
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:11,000
This time,

69
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:12,560
I will never leave again.

70
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:16,440
Tian Yan.

71
00:04:17,640 --> 00:04:19,000
I'm a monster.

72
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:21,160
I don't want to hurt you.

73
00:04:22,400 --> 00:04:22,800
I...

74
00:04:22,880 --> 00:04:24,400
I can't control myself.

75
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,200
It hurts.

76
00:04:32,080 --> 00:04:32,800
It hurts.

77
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:34,680
It hurts.

78
00:04:44,840 --> 00:04:45,920
Does it still hurt?

79
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:51,360
No.

80
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:52,320
It doesn't hurt anymore.

81
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:57,280
Pang Jingfu,

82
00:04:58,840 --> 00:04:59,720
I've given you the right

83
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:01,240
to hurt me a long time ago.

84
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:02,720
Because

85
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:06,240
I've loved you for a long time.

86
00:05:42,840 --> 00:05:44,240
What have I done?

87
00:05:48,280 --> 00:05:49,360
Tian Yan.

88
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:52,840
I wanted to protect you.

89
00:05:58,840 --> 00:06:00,160
People like me

90
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:02,160
will only

91
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:03,360
destroy you.

92
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:18,160
He's been abroad for the past two years,

93
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:20,760
secretly investigating his father's clues

94
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:22,760
while undergoing rehabilitation.

95
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:24,560
It's been a long time since the last attack.

96
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:27,080
Doctors say his willpower is remarkable.

97
00:06:27,280 --> 00:06:28,400
His condition is stable.

98
00:06:28,840 --> 00:06:29,840
How could it suddenly...

99
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:31,960
It's too strange.

100
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:34,120
Has he recently

101
00:06:34,440 --> 00:06:37,200
been exposed to anything that might trigger it?

102
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:39,000
Or

103
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:40,800
emotional stress?

104
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,880
Emotional stress...

105
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:44,480
That means...

106
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:47,880
Wait.

107
00:06:48,760 --> 00:06:49,520
Or...

108
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:51,040
Someone has taken action against him.

109
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:53,000
Pang Zhengsong?

110
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:54,080
It's hard to say.

111
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:56,120
That old guy is well hidden.

112
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:57,880
He has both hands and eyes.

113
00:06:59,080 --> 00:07:01,120
If he knows the boss is not dead

114
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:02,640
and is still investigating him secretly,

115
00:07:05,080 --> 00:07:06,840
someone might have secretly given him medicine.

116
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:16,880
No matter what the reason is,

117
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:19,880
and no matter what he'll be like next time,

118
00:07:20,520 --> 00:07:21,600
I won't leave him again.

119
00:07:22,840 --> 00:07:23,600
Yan.

120
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:26,120
I couldn't stay with him two years ago.

121
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:27,160
This time,

122
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:29,600
I won't let him stay alone in hell.

123
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:34,400
Pang Jingfu.

124
00:07:34,520 --> 00:07:35,480
It's me.

125
00:07:40,080 --> 00:07:41,040
Pang Jingfu.

126
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:44,800
He's not at home.

127
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:15,400
[Just like this,]

128
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:17,320
[don't come back.]

129
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:19,480
[I will only hurt you.]

130
00:08:22,080 --> 00:08:23,200
That's right, so

131
00:08:23,880 --> 00:08:25,080
you'll have to put in a bit more effort.

132
00:08:25,200 --> 00:08:25,840
Professor Li De.

133
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:26,640
Aira,

134
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:28,040
my student.

135
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:30,720
I would like to go over

136
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:32,240
the literature citation with you.

137
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:34,280
What a coincidence!

138
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:36,640
I've found you

139
00:08:36,640 --> 00:08:38,960
an even better reference.

140
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:41,000
Professor Bovis,

141
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,200
this is Ai La,

142
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:44,160
one of my best students.

143
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:45,960
Oh,

144
00:08:51,920 --> 00:08:53,200
Pang Zhengsong.

145
00:08:53,520 --> 00:08:56,240
Nice to meet you, Ai La.

146
00:08:56,760 --> 00:08:57,960
Or is this

147
00:08:58,320 --> 00:09:00,680
this Bovis just looks like him?

148
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:06,840
Professor Bovis,

149
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:07,760
it's an honor to meet you.

150
00:09:08,120 --> 00:09:10,800
I'm honored to cite your research.

151
00:09:10,920 --> 00:09:12,080
Do you have a moment now?

152
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:14,080
Could you sign this for me?

153
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:14,880
Of course.

154
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:15,880
Please.

155
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:20,320
It's my pleasure.

156
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:21,680
My dear.

157
00:09:36,040 --> 00:09:36,800
Is this okay?

158
00:09:38,160 --> 00:09:38,840
Thank you.

159
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:39,600
Thank you.

160
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:46,800
Two years ago,

161
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:49,760
Pang Zhengsong was rescued by his men

162
00:09:49,880 --> 00:09:51,440
on his way back to IPCO.

163
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:53,880
We haven't received any information about him since then.

164
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:57,200
Now he appears here so freely.

165
00:09:58,520 --> 00:09:59,600
Or

166
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:00,920
is this Bovis

167
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:02,640
just look like him?

168
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:09,240
It's you.

169
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:11,600
Pang Zhengsong.
